{"word":"G1654 - ἐλεημοσύνη - eleēmosýnē - el-eh-ay-mos-oo'-nay - Alms","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐλεημοσύνη</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>eleēmosýnē"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>el-eh-ay-mos-oo'-nay"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Alms"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தர்மம், பலன், பிச்சை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. mercy, pity"},{"paragraph":"2. the benefaction, a donation to the poor, alms"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1656 - ἔλεος - éleos - el'-eh-os/1656\">G1656</a>; <i>compassionateness</i>, that is, (as exercised towards the poor) <i>beneficence</i>, or (concretely) a <i>benefaction:</i> - alms (-deeds)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1653 - ἐλεέω - eleéō - el-eh-eh'-o/1653\">G1653</a>, <a href=\"#/G1654 - ἐλεημοσύνη - eleēmosýnē - el-eh-ay-mos-oo'-nay/1654\">G1654</a>, <a href=\"#/G1655 - ἐλεήμων - eleḗmōn - el-eh-ay'-mone/1655\">G1655</a>, <a href=\"#/G1656 - ἔλεος - éleos - el'-eh-os/1656\">G1656</a>, <a href=\"#/G415 - ἀνελεήμων - aneleḗmōn - an-eleh-ay'-mone/415\">G415</a>, <a href=\"#/G448 - ἀνίλεως - aníleōs - an-ee'-leh-oce/448\">G448</a>"}]}